Altair, Alpha Centauri, Sirius.

4
00:01:34,058 --> 00:01:36,143
Matt Shepherd?

5
00:01:36,227 --> 00:01:38,354
Ini hanya pesta dan dia mengajakku.

6
00:01:38,437 --> 00:01:41,273
- Dia baik sekali.
- Ya, mungkin bagimu.

7
00:01:41,356 --> 00:01:43,150
Kalian dapatkan hal menarik di sini?

8
00:01:43,233 --> 00:01:44,359
