1316
01:35:03,235 --> 01:35:05,737
Sayang, ayo kita pergi.

1317
01:35:05,820 --> 01:35:07,489
Ayo kita pergi sekarang.

1318
01:35:09,157 --> 01:35:11,325
- Beth...
- Selalu ada jalan keluar.

1319
01:35:11,409 --> 01:35:13,119
Kami akan baik-baik saja.

1320
01:35:13,202 --> 01:35:15,079
Anak pintar.

1321
