01:37:12,309 --> 01:37:14,853
Jalanan sangat ramai.
Kami tak akan berhasil.

1331
01:37:14,937 --> 01:37:17,898
Kalau gelombang datang,
sebaiknya kami di sini...

1332
01:37:17,981 --> 01:37:19,608
Karena dia suka di sini.

1333
01:37:19,691 --> 01:37:23,820
Kami berada di lantai 15,
jadi mungkin kami akan aman.

1334
01:37:23,903 --> 01:37:25,571
Ucapkan selamat tinggal
pada Jenny...

1335
01:37:25,655 --> 01:37:27,448
- Cepat jalan!
- Jenny!

1336
01:37:27,531 --> 01:37:29,408
- Cepat!
- Catie!

1337
01:37:29,491 --> 01:37:31,410
Ya Tuhan! Caitlin!

1338
01:37:31,493 --> 01:37:33,912
- Caitlin!
- Cepat jalan!

1339
01:37:37,415 --> 01:37:40,251
- Jenny!
- Ayo! Lebih cepat!

1340
01:37:41,044 --> 01:37:42,920
Tidak! Jangan!

