Leo!

1356
01:39:40,818 --> 01:39:42,945
Leo Beiderman! Leo!

1357
01:39:45,697 --> 01:39:46,949
Leo!

1358
01:39:54,414 --> 01:39:55,915
Leo!

1359
01:39:58,084 --> 01:39:59,919
Kalian tak ada waktu.
Pergilah sekarang.

