1444
01:49:33,101 --> 01:49:35,687
Dia memegang roket kecil.

1445
01:49:36,855 --> 01:49:39,607
Roketmu itu sangat canggih.

1446
01:49:39,691 --> 01:49:41,317
Dia tertawa.

1447
01:49:42,110 --> 01:49:44,237
Aku bisa mendengarnya.
Aku tahu.

1448
01:49:44,320 --> 01:49:46,530
Mariette...

1449
01:49:46,614 --> 01:49:49,116
Aku memeluk kalian berdua sekarang.

1450
01:49:49,199 --> 01:49:51,326
Aku merangkul kalian.

1451
01:49:52,119 --> 01:49:53,537
25 detik.

1452
01:49:53,620 --> 01:49:55,038
Bersiap menyinkronkan nuklir.

1453
01:49:55,121 --> 01:50:01,377
23, 22, 21...

1454
01:50:01,460 --> 01:50:07,299
20, 19, 18...

