01:50:13,763 --> 01:50:16,974
Suatu kehormatan bisa bekerja
bersamamu, Kapten.

1457
01:50:18,184 --> 01:50:20,519
Sama-sama, Andy.

1458
01:50:25,816 --> 01:50:29,069
Jadi anak baik, Oren.

